verbose_text: This section investigates the changes in PM 10 and PM 2.5 concentrations and in air pollutant (NO 2, SO 2, CO, O 3) levels at 65 air-pollution monitoring stations located all over Malaysia and include industrial (7), urban (10), suburban (36) and rural (12) sites.
